profile.bio: Writer and Free Thinker at Large. Wicked smart. Ruggedly handsome. Fun to be around. Science, Linux, & technology geek. The Cooking With Linux guy. Science fiction and fantasy writer. Editor. Opinionated. Anti-theist.
